I submitted ads 5 days ago. They are still pending. Is this timeframe for approval normal?

Hi Aldo, the ad approval process usually takes between 1-2 business days. Since it's been longer than that, it might be due to your account not being verified yet. If your account is new and not verified, please provide the following details by emailing adsupport@newsbreak.com with the subject line: Business Verification –
Company's full address
Company's legal entity name
Company's EHID or DUNS number
Primary contact person's name
Company's phone number
Once we receive this information, we will conduct a thorough review and update you on your account status.
We appreciate your cooperation in maintaining a secure and compliant advertising environment for all our partners.
